data.description: This home has all the upgrades and space you need! As soon as you open the front door you will be pleased to see the beautiful staircase, formal dining room with coffered ceilings, archways and the list goes on! Kitchen offers granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, island and pantry. 1 guest bedroom with access to a full bathroom on the main level, perfect for guests! Primary bedroom is a DREAM with plenty of space for large furniture, vaulted ceilings and an amazing custom closet with built-ins and an island. Separate soaker tub and tiled shower in bathroom. Guest bedrooms offer vaulted ceilings making the space feel much more open and grand + a custom built in closet in one of the rooms. Covered back patio and fenced in yard. This home is move in ready!
